To find a project: 

Search the genus on BioProject 

Open up the project page and Google it (or any citations listed) to try to find the original citation it is paired with. 

To get a list of SRA accessions:

If the year is correct, click on its SRA experiments (should be under 'Number of Links.'

Click Send results to Run selector. 

Under Download, click Accession List. This will send all the SRAs associated with the BioProject to a .txt file. 

Upload the .txt file to a server and direct the Prefetch script to this. 
